{"tid":1324781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我個廚房佬細佬同廢老講:你游水落英國人地方係咪叛國?係咪出賣中國人?係咪漢奸","createTime":"2019-07-16T16:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T12:46:07.000Z","uid":26601,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cfd5b3fabdc61675c734b29f7c1fe6631e888041","tid":1324781,"uid":26601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:06:14.000Z","msg":"話說我個廢老家父一日到黑睇大陸d 解放劇<br />\n日日都話中國幾強大，美國好廢<br />\n我細佬忍唔住同佢講：<br />\n你又講到自己咁愛國，咁自豪做中國人<br />\n點解你當年游水落黎英國人既地方？<br />\n你係咪出賣中國人？<br />\n你係咪漢奸？<br />\n<br />\n廢老聽到後焗到面紅行路都成問題<br />\n全家立即制止佢繼續講落去<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界其實唔係蠢人多<br />\n華人世界既特產係賤人同自私既人"},{"pid":"8c23fa5116c91dcced1c19b195455240b76bea16","tid":1324781,"uid":175695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:08:37.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"4a862a9719700d931e831c1edff590158a75dd28","tid":1324781,"uid":26601,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:09:02.000Z","msg":"上一代廢老根本無資格屌我地<br />\n除非佢地肯上去公安局自首當年叛國投靠英國，勾結外國勢力"},{"pid":"146b383fe8c5b8057d27c0177fbad7a7f302aa4a","tid":1324781,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:09:32.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e653a7a1110b51ace06c17c839bca6f5781133f","tid":1324781,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:18:25.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻阻你，用外國勢力救救前線！<br />\n<br />\n  <span style=\"color: red;\">[我都要攬炒]一齊上twitter將黑警權力過大揚威國際，警告遊客不要來港旅遊！！！ </span><br />\n<br />\n文字template係#72！！！照copy就得！！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1324656/page/1！！\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1324656/page/1！！</a>"},{"pid":"48e29fdc17efe1c23bb7bea44d8fd2f0140734f0","tid":1324781,"uid":71037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:19:59.000Z","msg":"唔應該收聲<br />\n應該non-stop 瘋狂鬧，鬧到佢爆血管"},{"